 A LIGHTER NOTE 
</P>
<P>
 Among the many parties thrown at the state Republican Party convention over 
the weekend, "Name That Brown" night stood out. Invitations to the two-hour 
poolside event included this series of mock "TV Guide" listings poking fun at 
Democrat Kathleen Brown's candidacy: "The Wheel of Misfortune," "The Price 
Isn't Right," "Let's Make Any Deal" and "California in Jeopardy." 
