<DOCNO> LA092094-0185 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 081000 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 20, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
