<P>
GINGRICH CAMPAIGN FINED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Federal Election Commission has fined House Republican Whip Newt 
Gingrich's 1992 campaign committee $3,800 for failing to comply with campaign 
finance laws. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
