 While browsing in an upscale antique/gift shop, reader Karen Newman of L.A. 
overheard a man talking to his young son about a beautiful antique French box. 
Obviously trying to teach the boy about valuable antiques and hoping to ensure 
that the youngster would handle the box carefully, the father explained: "It's 
very, very old." 
